            <p>I don&#8217;t believe this is a problem, if you go ahead and make the container element fullscreen.</p>
<p>The one containing both the controls and the video. This might actually make it easier to style the video and the controls in fullscreen.</p>
<p>This is what I&#8217;m currently doing, as I&#8217;m in the process of making a custom video player as well.</p>

